title: Eps. 120 - You Can't Have My Check
description:
Handouts and shortcuts, two words that the guys can’t stand ! This week on the podcast CJ goes off about one of his pet peeves. People asking for a handout or trying to take a short cut. You have a dream and you have a goal but you’re not willing to go through the fire to make it happen. The guys give tips on what to do and what not to do while trying to blow up, how to reach out to high profile people for an opportunity, and what absolutely NOT to do to try to get traction in your business. Keep in mind that there are NO shortcuts and NO handouts.
 Time Stamped Topics:
  [09:20] - No shortcut
 [18:40] - ET Going Gorilla
 [32:47] - You Can’t Have My Check
 [46:28] - Show Your Work
 [56:50] - Ask ET
 [1:20:00] - Nugget of The Day
  Listener Perks:
  Organifi is giving our listeners 20% off of their order just use the promo code “SUCCESS”. Their superfood green juice powder allows you to get your greens anytime anywhere while on the go.
 Hello Fresh is giving our listeners $30 off your first week of deliveries just use the code “SUCCESS30”
  The Secrets To Success:
  “Invited guests are welcomed best.”
 “Excellence attracts excellence.”
 “When people are happy their productivity isn’t the same.”
 “Nothing too soon is a blessing.”
 “Success has an equation and you have to follow the equation and show your work.”
